Remember last year when we both got the August predictions?  That didn&#39;t pan out, so i wouldn&#39;t take what they say too seriously.  They have never said anything that came true yet, i don&#39;t think they can.

I&#39;m pretty sure that they can&#39;t tell the future, so when they say stuff i think they are just messing with us to see what we do with the information.  They might even be laughing at us !

-Steve



